Job Title: AI Engineer
Location: Central London
Role Type: Permanent
Work Schedule: Initially in-office, with flexibility after the first few months

Shape the future of AI in telecommunications with our client who is seeking a Senior AI Engineer to lead the development of our multi-lingual Telco LLM and design scalable, high-performance systems for next-gen telecom solutions.

What You'll Do:

    Build robust, fault-tolerant backend systems for AI integration.
    Work with ML experts to deploy large language models.
    Develop event-driven architectures and optimize AI performance.

What You Bring:

    5+ years of backend development experience.
    Expertise in distributed systems, APIs, and AI/ML integration.
    Passion for cutting-edge AI technologies.
    Familiarity with ML concepts and terminology
    Experience in the telecommunications industry.(Preferred)
    Knowledge of multi-lingual language processing systems.(Preferred)

